Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
Set within the highly successful master planned 'Emerald Lakes' community, opportunities exist to lease the final remaining ground floor retail tenancies. The Boulevard retail precinct consists of a mix retail, medical, cafe and restaurants in over 20 tenancies, and is surrounded by corporate office space and permanent residential buildings.

Centrally located, The Town Centre benefits from easy access to the M1 (Nerang exit), is in close proximity to Nerang Train Station and walking distance to Metricon Stadium, RACQ Royal Pines, Emerald Lakes Golf Centre and next door to Emmanuel College.

Remaining spaces include;
 - 207sqm* with option to be split. Includes partial ex-grocer fit-out with cool room, display fridge and rear storage room
- 44.8sqm* centrally positioned ground floor tenancy with grease trap well suited to boutique F&B retail, specialist medical or office
- 131sqm* cold shell tenancy in centre of village arcade, suited to varied uses including indoor recreation (STCA)

- Ample on-site parking available for clients and customers
- Weekly Thursday Twilight markets held within the village
- Consistent traffic flow from both local residents and customers of surrounding services

Final tenancies seeking to be activated, contact marketing agents to discuss your options and arrange an on-site inspection.

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
Set within the highly successful master planned 'Emerald Lakes' community, opportunities exist to lease high quality office space. The Town Centre commercial building consists of 4 levels of office space and is surrounded by residential and retail buildings.

Available options;
* 315 sqm- ground floor, fully fitted, high quality tenancy including furniture and workstations. 

* 364sqm- Level 3, full high quality fitout in place, great natural light and views all around.

* 150-387sqm- Level 3, open plan tenancy which can be split to suit. Fitout incentives on offer.

* 200-413sqm- Level 4, open plan tenancy which can be split to suit. Fitout incentives on offer.

* 1,067sqm- Level 5, exclusive whole top floor. Full corporate fitout in place including furniture. Great views and natural light throughout.

3d walkthroughs available in link for all fitted tenancies.

For further information including plans or to arrange an inspection please contact the exclusive agent.
